quran[50]{c,v,t}:
  15,50,(Ubazise) nokokuba isohlwayo saM sibuhlungu kanobom
  15,51,Ke kaloku baxelele ngamandwendwe kaIbrâhîm (aye eziingelosi)
  15,52,"Athi akungena kwakhe, athi: “Salâm” (uxolo). UIbrâhîm wathi: “Inene thina siyanoyika.”"
  15,53,"Athi wona: “Musa ukoyika! “Sikuphathele iindaba ezivuyisayo zomntwana oyinkwenkwe, onolwazi oluninzi nobulumko.”"
  15,54,"UIbrâhîm wathi: “Nindiphathele iindaba ezivuyisayo ekubeni ukwaluphala sele kundifumene (kangaka)? Ziyintoni ezo ndaba zenu?”"
  15,55,"Athi wona (amandwendwe lawo): “Sikuphathele iindaba ezivuyisayo ngenyaniso, musa ukuba ngomnye wabo bangenathemba.”"
  15,56,"UIbrâhîm wathi: “Ngubani na olahla ithemba lenceba yeNkosi yakhe ngaphandle kwalowo ulahlekileyo?”"
  15,57,"(UIbrâhîm wathi): “Kanti uyintoni umbandela enize ngawo kanye kanye nina ziThunywa?”"
  15,58,"Zathi zona: “Thina sithunyelwe kubantu abangabenzi bobubi"
  15,59,"“Bangcole bonke ngaphandle kosapho lukaLût, lona ke ngokuqinisekileyo siya kulusindisa ekutshatyalalisweni"
  15,60,"Ngaphandle komkakhe, yena lowo sele simisele okokuba uya kuba ngomnye wabo baza kushiyeka ngemva.”"
  15,61,Ke kaloku izithunywa ezo zisakufika kusapho lukaLût
  15,62,"Wathi yena: “Inene ningabantu endingabaziyo mna.”"
  15,63,"Zathi zona: “Yeha! Size kuwe ngeso sohlwayo bebesoloko besithandabuza"
  15,64,Kananjalo sikuzisele inyaniso yaye sithetha inyaniso
  15,65,"Ke wena hamba ngenxalenye yobusuku nosapho lwakho, uze wena uhambe ngemva kwalo, maze kungabikho namnye kuni unyeka ngemva koko hambani niye apho niyalelwe ukuba niye khona.”"
  15,66,Ke kaloku Thina Sawenza wazeka kuye lo mmiselo wokuba iingcambu zabo bangaboni ziza kuncothulwa ekuseni ngonyezi (kusemyama)
  15,67,"Abemi besixeko (iSodom neGomora) beza bevuya (besakuva ukuba kukho amadodana amahle afikileyo kwaLût, phofu benenjongo ezikukungcola ngawo)"
  15,68,"ULût wathi: “Inene ezi ziindwendwe zam. Musani ukundihlaza kuzo"
  15,69,Kananjalo yoyikani uAllâh.”
  15,70,"Bathi bona: “Asizanga sikwalele na ukuba wena ungonwabisi okanye ukhusele nabani na endalweni?”"
  15,71,"ULût wathi: “Izizo ezi iintombi zam nje (eninokuzitshata), ukuba kunyanzelekile nenze le nto (nifuna ukuyenza)?”"
  15,72,"Inene Ndifunga6 ngobomi bakho (Muhammad) ekunxileni kwabo bubundlobongela babo, babefathula ngobumfama"
  15,73,Kanye njengoko (abakwaSâlih) bafunyanwa (sisohlwayo) ukuphuma kwelanga
  15,74,Sayiphethula (iSodom) yajonga ezantsi Sathulula imvula yamatye odongwe olutshisiweyo phezu kwabo
  15,75,Inene! Kulo eli (bali) kukho imiqondiso kwabo babonayo
  15,76,"Kananjalo izixeko ezo zazimi kuhola wendlela (ophakathi kweMakkah neSiriya, ndawo leyo namhlanje yaziwa ngokuba yiDead Sea)"
  15,77,"Inene, kwesi sehlo kukho umqondiso kwabakholwayo"
  15,78,Ke kaloku nabemi basezinkunini7 babekwangabagabadeli
  15,79,"Thina ke Sathabatha impindezelo kubo. Bona (nabaseSodom) ababesendleleni enguhola ukuba babonwe, (bacace) gca"
  15,80,Kananjalo nabemi basemaweni babaphika abaProfeti
  15,81,Ke kaloku Sabanika Thina imiqondiso yeThu kodwa abakholwa kuyo
  15,82,Bona babesakha imizi yabo ezintabeni
  15,83,Kodwa sona isohlwayo sabafumana ekuseni ngesifingo
  15,84,Ke kaloku konke ababekusebenzele akuzanga kubancede nganto
  15,85,"Thina ke ASizanga Sidale amazulu nomhlaba nako konke okuphakathi apho ngaphandle kokuwadalela inyaniso. Kananjalo iYure yona iyeza ngokwenene, ke (wena Muhammad) yiba ngathi awuziboni iziphoso zabo ubuye ngenceba nemfesane (kubo)"
  15,86,"Inene iNkosi yakho nguMdali, uSolwazi"
  15,87,Inene Thina Sikuphe iSab’an minal mathâni8 ne’Kur’ân yonke
  15,88,"Ke kaloku wena maze amehlo akho angajameli izinto eSiziphe abathile kubo (abangakholwayo), ungabi buhlungu nokuba buhlungu ngazo. Yiba nenceba kwabakholwayo (amaMuslim)"
  15,89,"Yithi\tkubo\t(Muhammad):\t“Mna\tndinguMlumkisi ngokusekuhleni"
  15,90,Njengoko Sithumele kubahlula-hluli
  15,91,"Abenza\ti’Kur’ân\tibe\tzizahlulo\tngezahlulo\t(bakholwe kwinxalenye yayo bangakholwa kwenye)"
  15,92,"Inene (Ndifunga) ngeNkosi yakho (Muhammad), Siza kubabiza bonke beze embuzweni (ngezenzo zabo)"
  15,93,Ngako konke oko bakwenzayo
  15,94,"Wena ke vakalisa ngaphandle [ungawufihli (uMyalezo ka- Allâh)] lowo uyalelwe ngawo. Uzikhwebule kubakhonzi bezithixo"
  15,95,Inene Thina Siya kukwenza wanele uwedwa ngokuchasene nabagculeli
  15,96,"Abayamanisa omnye uthixo kuAllâh, kodwa baza kwazi kungekudala"
  15,97,"Inene, Thina Siyazi okokuba intliziyo yakho icinezelekile ngenxa yoko bakuthethayo"
  15,98,"Ke wena zukisa ngendumiso iNkosi yakho, ube ngomnye wabo baqubudayo kuYo"
  15,99,Uyinqule iNkosi yakho kananjalo kude kufike isiqinisekiso esiyinyani (ukufa)